Text: Many thanks.  Many excellent books, and as stated but BebeCakes, some that have either not been available before and others that have not been seeded.  Other uploads by BebeCakes are very good as well, but I will only comment here.  Thanks again for taking the time to upload these.

Indeed!  Some of the books are very hard to find online, and some of the previous ones are no longer shared. :) 

Glad you like it!  Wow. :)
